The requirements for creating a conversational chatbot and voice searching is:

Python version 3+
Chatterbot
chatterbot-corpus
SpeechRecognition
googleapiclient
webbrowser
Tkinter

How to install Pip in windows:
Download "get-pip.py" to a folder on your computer. Open a command prompt window and navigate to the folder containing get-pip.py. 
Then run python get-pip.py. This will install pip.
Then type "pip freeze" you will see what modules are installed in your python.

NOTE:
How to install modules in Windows is by using pip command 
    pip install modulename
        eg: pip install chatterbot
